# Arc CCTP Bridge — Environment Variables
#
# This app uses browser wallets (MetaMask, EIP-6963 standard).
# No environment variables are required to run the app.
#
# Optional: override public RPC endpoints with private/custom URLs.
# NEXT_PUBLIC_ARC_RPC_URL=https://rpc.testnet.arc.network
# NEXT_PUBLIC_ETH_SEPOLIA_RPC_URL=https://...
